      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and will best suit a buyer who appreciates value, practicality, and the chance to put their own touch on it. Priced to sell, this is a straightforward opportunity for someone seeking low-cost ownership without unnecessary markup.",
