    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project or commuter with strong fundamentals. Engine fires up and runs, transmission engages, and the car moves out well with responsive steering and a composed chassis for its age. Not a showpiece, but it has the kind of honest, mechanical feel that makes it a practical fixer-upper, parts runner, or first car for someone handy. A great opportunity to get into a running vehicle at an affordable price.",
